nvu: nvu (a complete Web Authoring System)
nvu:
nvu: Nvu (pronounced N-view, for a "new view") is a complete Web Authoring
nvu: System that combines web file management and easy-to-use WYSIWYG
nvu: (What You See Is What You Get) web page editing.  Nvu is designed to
nvu: be extremely easy to use, making it ideal for non-technical computer
nvu: users who want to create an attractive, professional-looking web site
nvu: without needing to know HTML or web coding.
